How to do
Service Projects
1. Go to our website or link tree for our at-home service
projects!
2. Look through our selection of service projects ranging
from online work, DIY projects, and community
support.
3. To get your hours, you must submit photo/video
proof. Photos must have a timer throughout the
process or you may film a timelapse of the process.
4. Have fun and serve the community during quarantine!
https://tinyurl.com/frkcAtHomeService
